<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FORFEO LAB | Une division de FORFEO INC.</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/premium-dashboard.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/home-premium.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="blob-container"><div class="blob blob-1"></div><div class="blob blob-2"></div></div>

    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg fixed-top navbar-premium py-2">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">
                <img src="/images/logo-forfeo.png" class="logo-img" alt="Forfeo Logo">
                <span class="brand-lab-neon">LAB</span>
            </a>
            
            <button class="navbar-toggler border-0" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav"><span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span></button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto gap-3 align-items-center">
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/login">Connexion</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item d-flex gap-2">
                        <a class="btn btn-outline-primary rounded-pill px-3 fw-bold" href="/register?role=ambassadeur">Espace Ambassadeur</a>
                        <a class="btn btn-primary rounded-pill px-3 fw-bold shadow-sm" href="/register?role=entreprise">Espace Entreprise</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <section class="hero-section d-flex align-items-center" style="min-height: 90vh; padding-top: 100px;">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <h1 class="display-3 fw-bolder mb-4">L'expérience client <span style="color: #0061ff;">mesurable.</span></h1>
                    <p class="lead text-muted mb-5">
                        FORFEO LAB permet aux entreprises d'évaluer la qualité de leurs services grâce à des audits mystères et de réaliser des <strong>sondages clients</strong> certifiés.
                    </p>
                    <a href="/register?role=entreprise" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg rounded-pill px-5 shadow-lg fw-bold">Commencer</a>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <div class="mockup-3d p-4 bg-white">
                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-4 pb-3 border-bottom">
                            <h5 class="fw-bold m-0">Tableau de bord</h5>
                            <span class="badge bg-success">Score: 94%</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-primary text-white p-3 rounded-3 d-flex align-items-center gap-3 shadow-sm badge-flash-wow">
                            <i class="bi bi-stars fs-3"></i>
                            <div><div class="fw-bold">Nouveau Sondage</div><small>Réponses en direct</small></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-5 bg-light">
        <div class="container text-center">
            <h2 class="fw-bold mb-5">Pourquoi évaluer vos services ?</h2>
            <div class="row g-4">
                <div class="col-md-4"><h2 class="display-4 fw-bold text-primary">86%</h2><p>paient plus pour un meilleur service.</p></div>
                <div class="col-md-4"><h2 class="display-4 fw-bold text-primary">1/3</h2><p>quittent après une erreur.</p></div>
                <div class="col-md-4"><h2 class="display-4 fw-bold text-primary">Loi 25</h2><p>Conformité totale Québec.</p></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="py-5 bg-white border-top mt-auto">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-start mb-3">
                        <img src="/images/logo-forfeo.png" height="35">
                        <span class="brand-lab-neon" style="font-size: 10px; margin-left: 5px;">LAB</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="small text-muted">Forfeo Lab est une division de <strong>FORFEO INC.</strong>, entreprise enregistrée au Québec. Conformité Loi 25 assurée.</p>
                    <p class="small text-muted"><a href="/politique-confidentialite">Politique de confidentialité</a> | <a href="/conditions-utilisation">Conditions</a></p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 text-md-end">
                    <p class="small text-muted">Les ambassadeurs sont des travailleurs autonomes indépendants.</p>
                    <p class="small text-muted">© 2025 FORFEO INC.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
    <%- include('partials/forfy') %>
</body>
</html>
